s://lihkg.com/thread/1497032/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手推下<br />\n外國巴絲你地可以做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T20:07:02.000Z","msg":"已push"},{"pid":"9c47ff79583fafca65d22c943f25130476c9134c","tid":1496212,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33ff1a0d1d9ae1cbadf2dfe1bacda4fadccfe32b","tid":1496212,"uid":225146,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭相比之下已經係冇咁多中國人<br />\n都咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T20:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛爾蘭先多"},{"pid":"a878fcebb5361cb90c2351dce54eebf519c7caa0","tid":1496212,"uid":283240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T20:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfdj36V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgfdj36V.png&h=bbac7f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.irishtimes.com/business/economy/chinese-fdi-to-ireland-jumps-75-as-it-bucks-global-trend-1.3991840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irishtimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fchinese-fdi-to-ireland-jumps-75-as-it-bucks-global-trend-1.3991840&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=8043b685\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.irishtimes.com/business/economy/chinese-fdi-to-ireland-jumps-75-as-it-bucks-global-trend-1.3991840</a><br />\n<br />\n在愛爾蘭的外國投資大陸就快追到美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開放投資移民 &gt;&gt; 好多大陸人過黎同當地發展商集資起屋苑<br />\n不停招收大陸學生 &gt;&gt; 愛爾蘭d大學排名唔高又容易入，英文教學，但平過英國學費好多"},{"pid":"e112f3c39bdd204ef0a543b5d898febd35903c6f","tid":1496212,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T20:18:02.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭差佬戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"aeb3e01ba721e734902a12b43d352ac782705af6","tid":1496212,"uid":283240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T20:34:01.000Z","msg":"呢度有好多大中華膠<br />\n<br />\n頭號賣港大中華膠 - Kam Chin 錢錦倫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iNBRaPZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiNBRaPZ.jpg&h=4445d516&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n錢錦倫搞左個愛中友好協會，自己做主席，做埋僑胞聯絡人，幫中共同中國大使館收風！<a href=\"http://www.icsgalway.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.icsgalway.org%2F&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=10c75721\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.icsgalway.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本身80年代做體育老師，臨中英談判前移民愛爾蘭，之後過到黎英文又講到1999 只可以做餐館 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後就有餐館經驗，可以做返老本行教書，今次係開學校教人catering<br />\n呢間&gt;&gt; <a href=\"http://www.icsgalway.org/education/iihcs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.icsgalway.org%2Feducation%2Fiihcs%2F&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5a39ccf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.icsgalway.org/education/iihcs/</a><br />\n<br />\n再聯同香港既大佬搞愛爾蘭留學&gt;&gt; <a href=\"http://www.iiec.com.hk/zh_HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iiec.com.hk%2Fzh_HK%2F&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=c89b467a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.iiec.com.hk/zh_HK/</a><br />\n搵香港同大陸學生去自己間學校留學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正唔正規唔知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾年成日返香港呃香港人投資移民玩集資, 集資expand間學校<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FRVcAXSNFyI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFRVcAXSNFyI&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=634be2a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FRVcAXSNFyI</a>"},{"pid":"9267008fa6d1bc848865458a5ea52c82aef5eecd","tid":1496212,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit