es/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我地希望繼續 招募 18 區嘅 Fact check 戰士 入黎幫手<br />\n一齊將你果區區議員/社區主任過往幾年嘅 貢獻 記錄得一清二楚！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAdmin 工作唔一定繁重，相反因為 Admin 們各自都有嘢忙，所以更加要多啲人互相 Cover。<br />\n有興趣嘅手足可以先入黎公海 TG group 了解下先再申請加入 Admin<br />\n<br />\n全民 Fact Check<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n==============================================<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n[選區事實處 網站] <a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.github.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.github.io&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=058cf311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.github.io</a><br />\n[公海 TG] <a href=\"https://t.me/DistrictsFactCheck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDistrictsFactCheck&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=3ef70d2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DistrictsFactCheck</a><br />\n[單筆報料] <a href=\"https://forms.gle/KUjYP3G71sGfWiS97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FKUjYP3G71sGfWiS97&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2LdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=ec28cf4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/KUjYP3G71sGfWiS97</a><br />\n==============================================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LKvtz3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%